Enum dnnl.query

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<dnnl.query>
      • org.bytedeco.dnnl.global.dnnl.query
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<dnnl.query>
    Enclosing class:
    dnnl

    @Namespace(value="dnnl")
public static enum dnnl.query
extends Enum<dnnl.query>
    \} dnnl_api_rnn

    \addtogroup dnnl_api_primitives_common \{

    Primitive descriptor query specification. In general, queries are not used with the C++ API because most queries are implemented as class members. See \ref dnnl_query_t for more information.
